  "texts": [
    "The third category is called current academic performance features, which include course information, years of enrolment, attendance, assignment, laboratory and final grade, and GPA, etc.",
    "The last category is called student's learning behavior and interaction data, such as web page clicking, number of logins, total online time, number of uploading/downloading and visiting discussion forums, number of submitted assessments, and video interaction data (playback speed, pauses, seek back, seek forward, and video completed), etc.",
    "Some of the features used in the research have the same meaning, but are labeled differently.",
    "These are only a few of the many features that can be used to predict student's academic performance.",
    "A summary of the feature's categories used in the related studies for performance prediction is provided in Table 11."
